---

Approval Workflow

Objects requiring approval enter an approval queue.

Reviewer examines:

Purpose

Relationships

Technical accuracy

Revision summary

Dependencies

Approval options:

Approve

Request Changes

Reject

Deferred

Approval automatically:

Updates version number.

Creates revision history.

Records approver.

Records timestamp.

Updates dependent objects.

Notifies affected users.

